ing it here because there are various incomprehensible conspiracy theories =
about AMC short sellers, =E2=80=9Cphantom shares,=E2=80=9D etc., and so it =
is just about possible to say =E2=80=9Caha, issuing an APE dividend will fl=
ush out all the phantom shares and catch the nefarious short sellers!=E2=80=
=9D I don=E2=80=99t know. Here=E2=80=99s  the Wall Street Journal:
