We  talked about the  deli a  lot last  year. Now it is a bioplastics compa=
ny. The consensus around the deli was that it was not=C2=A0really=C2=A0a $1=
00 million publicly traded deli: It was a shell company that would eventual=
ly be used to take some other weird company public, and the deli was just s=
ort of a placeholder. That all happened pretty much as expected.

