  [3] Why? I don=E2=80=99t know. It is conventional to say that shareholder=
s don=E2=80=99t want to be diluted, and I guess that is right, but it=E2=80=
=99s kind of weird: If the stock is soaring for no reason, it is accretive =
for existing shareholders to issue more stock. (I suppose if you=E2=80=99re=
 an existing shareholder you might disagree that the stock is soaring for n=
