. AMC stock is mostly held by retail investors, and it is widely assumed th=
at retail shareholders mostly don=E2=80=99t vote their stock. And in fact i=
f you look at the results of AMC=E2=80=99s shareholder voting this year =E2=
=80=94 on routine matters like electing directors and approving executive p=
ay =E2=80=94 only about 145 million shares (out of 516 million) were actual=
